               <p>I saw the prisoner take the glass from the prosecutor's door, I made way for him to come by; I told the prosecutor, I lost sight of the prisoner that while, we pursued him, I saw the prisoner again, and he had not the glass.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I never saw the glass.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called three witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
